    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 per MRL 2 requirements. Validation evidence demonstrates CFD model predictions of relative hemolysis index and pressure head are within acceptance thresholds across the full COU operating envelope. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: uncertainty quantification has been declared for this assessment; sensitivity analysis documentation is pending completion in the next revision cycle.",
